ğŸ”¥ VERY IMPORTANT REALIZATION
This line ğŸ‘‡
return 1 if curr_sum == k else 0
does NOT mean:
â€œReturn the final answerâ€
It means:
â€œDoes THIS PARTICULAR subsequence count as 1 or 0?â€
The real counting happens when recursion unwinds and adds everything up.
